\v 28 \wj “Les \+w dijo|strong="G3004"\+w*: ‘\+w Un|strong="G3588"\+w* \+w enemigo|strong="G2190"\+w* ha \+w hecho|strong="G4160"\+w* \+w esto|strong="G3778"\+w*’. \wj*  
